reviewText: Usually jazzercise has more music and dancey moves. This tape also uses resistance tubing during many of the segments which I don't own

Sculpted arms, tight abs,firm and shapely thighs. they CAN be yours withBody Sculpting by Jazzercise. A perfect supplement to your aerobic fitness program, jazzercise's new resistance workout redefines your body by isolating specific muscles during a focused 50 minutecalorie and fat burning training session led by Jazzercise founder Judy Sheppard Missett, and Jazzercise instructors Chere Taylor van Ligten & Susan Slaughter
